<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1892-10-12T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1892-10-12T00:00:00-05:00" n="512" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d512">
                    <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Foster</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Scruggs</persName>.</hi></head>
                    <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                    <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Department
                                    of State</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1892-10-12"><hi rend="italic">October 12,
                            1892</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                    <p>Mr. Foster directs Mr. Scruggs to recognize the new government, provided it
                        is accepted by the people in possession of the power of the nation and fully
                        established; he asks to be informed of action taken.</p>
                </div>
                </body></text></TEI>